        <ul>
          <li>Condition analysis of vintage football shirts based on uploaded photos</li>
          <li>Estimated market valuations based on current market data</li>
          <li>Product code verification assistance</li>
          <li>Collection management tools</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>AI valuations are not guarantees.</strong> The Service provides estimates based on available data and AI analysis. We do not guarantee:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>The accuracy of any valuation</li>
          <li>That a shirt will sell for the estimated price</li>
          <li>The authenticity of any item</li>
          <li>The completeness of our product code database</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, KitTicker shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Service.
        </p>
        
        <h2>4. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>You agree to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide accurate photos for valuation</li>
          <li>Not use the Service for fraudulent purposes</li>
          <li>Not attempt to manipulate or deceive the AI system</li>
          <li>Not upload images you do not have rights to</li>
          <li>Maintain the security of your account</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All content, branding, and technology of KitTicker are owned by us or our licensors. You retain ownership of photos you upload, but grant us a license to process them for providing the Service.
        </p>
        
        <h2>6. Subscriptions and Payments</h2>
        <p>
          Paid subscriptions are billed monthly or annually via Lemon Squeezy. Refunds are handled according to our refund policy. Credits are non-refundable and expire at the end of each billing period unless otherwise stated.
        </p>
        
        <h2>7. Account Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We may suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms. You may delete your account at any time through your account settings or by contacting support.
        </p>
        
        <h2>8. Modifications to Service</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the Service at any time. We will provide reasonable notice for significant changes.
        </p>
        
        <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of [Jurisdiction]. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of [Jurisdiction].
        </p>
        
        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these Terms, contact us at:<br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@kitticker.com">legal@kitticker.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
